1
00:01:56,820 --> 00:02:02,820
=The Unexpected Marriage=

2
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:07,660
=Episode 12=

3
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:13,620
Let go.

4
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,380
Stand up and take a look.

5
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:31,520
You scared me.

6
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:34,780
It's so shallow.

7
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:49,340
What were you doing?

8
00:02:49,660 --> 00:02:50,980
Our body is given by our parents.

9
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:52,100
How can you destroy it at will?

10
00:02:52,340 --> 00:02:55,100
If you don't want to live anymore,
don't drag others to die with you.

11
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:57,340
When did I drag you?

12
00:02:57,340 --> 00:02:59,140
Do you know that if you commit suicide,
you will go to hell

13
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:00,140
and suffer endlessly?

14
00:03:00,340 --> 00:03:01,460
If the water was a little deeper,

15
00:03:01,460 --> 00:03:02,460
we'd have met in the underworld.

16
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:04,020
I...

17
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:06,460
- This...
- In the blink of an eye,

18
00:03:06,740 --> 00:03:07,780
what happened?

19
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:18,020
Go back and think about it carefully.

20
00:03:18,260 --> 00:03:19,220
Don't try to kill yourself again.

21
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:34,340
Changsheng.

22
00:03:34,540 --> 00:03:35,860
Do you like these flowers?

23
00:03:35,860 --> 00:03:37,660
Orchids are found everywhere in Fuyu.

24
00:03:38,340 --> 00:03:39,420
But in Great Tang,

25
00:03:39,420 --> 00:03:41,300
they become the precious Fuirena.

26
00:03:41,780 --> 00:03:42,900
I can't afford it.

27
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:46,300
Changsheng.

28
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,020
I asked the cook to make you
squirrel-shaped mandarin fish.

29
00:03:48,300 --> 00:03:49,500
I'll send it to you in the evening.

30
00:03:49,500 --> 00:03:50,500
Let's dine together.

31
00:03:51,460 --> 00:03:52,700
Thank you, Your Highness.

32
00:03:52,940 --> 00:03:54,500
I'm not hungry yet,
so I'll go back to the room.

33
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,460
Book...

34
00:04:02,940 --> 00:04:04,140
Your Highness, is there anything else?

35
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:05,820
The welcome dinner will be held tomorrow.

36
00:04:06,100 --> 00:04:07,740
In previous years,
people would ask the organizer

37
00:04:07,740 --> 00:04:08,580
to perform before the Emperor.

38
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:10,100
You're new here.

39
00:04:10,100 --> 00:04:11,500
There must be someone with bad intentions.

40
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:12,380
If you don't want to,

41
00:04:12,380 --> 00:04:13,820
just refuse without hesitation.

42
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:15,540
I'll handle the rest.

43
00:04:16,020 --> 00:04:17,140
Perform before the Emperor?

44
00:04:18,020 --> 00:04:19,340
This kind of thing doesn't bother me.

45
00:04:19,540 --> 00:04:20,860
It seems that you're well prepared.

46
00:04:21,340 --> 00:04:22,180
I won't tell you.

47
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:23,500
Besides,

48
00:04:23,660 --> 00:04:24,900
I'm going to start practicing now.

49
00:04:25,300 --> 00:04:26,140
Please go back.

50
00:04:27,620 --> 00:04:28,460
All right.

51
00:04:49,940 --> 00:04:52,540
(Fine Spirits of the Universe)

52
00:04:55,660 --> 00:04:57,620
He called the small pond a lake.

53
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:02,300
Please forgive me, Princess Royal.

54
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:04,820
It's fine.

55
00:05:04,820 --> 00:05:05,660
Leave me first.

56
00:05:06,180 --> 00:05:07,020
Yes.

57
00:05:14,780 --> 00:05:15,700
Put it there.

58
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:16,900
Princess Royal.

59
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:18,780
Drink the ginger soup while it's hot.

60
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:29,140
Did you suddenly think of something?

61
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:33,580
Go check

62
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:34,900
who was the man in the palace today.

63
00:05:35,500 --> 00:05:36,340
Yes.

64
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:37,700
After checking,

65
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:38,900
will he be severely punished?

66
00:05:39,100 --> 00:05:40,380
Just check it first.

67
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,460
(Huadeng Pavilion)

68
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,620
Jinyan, come here.

69
00:05:56,820 --> 00:05:57,660
Let me tell you.

70
00:05:57,940 --> 00:05:58,780
Help me prepare.

71
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:02,020
Understand?

72
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:03,260
Your Highness.

73
00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:04,540
What do you want these for?

74
00:06:04,540 --> 00:06:06,940
His Highness had told me
before coming to Great Tang

75
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:08,140
that we should proceed with caution.

76
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,260
I have my own reason

77
00:06:09,260 --> 00:06:10,180
for doing this.

78
00:06:10,540 --> 00:06:12,180
You, Youyong and Youmou,

79
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,180
go help me get prepared.

80
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:14,020
- Yes.
- Yes.

81
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:15,860
Okay, go quickly.

82
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:17,820
Remember to tell Youyong and Youmou

83
00:06:18,020 --> 00:06:18,940
to be smart.

84
00:06:18,940 --> 00:06:19,940
Don't be noticed.

85
00:06:31,540 --> 00:06:33,700
(Longevity Hall)

86
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,580
(Peace in All the World)

87
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,220
Changsheng.

88
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:47,980
The one above is Consort De.

89
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:49,380
She's the head of the harem now

90
00:06:49,700 --> 00:06:51,220
and also the biological mother
of Prince Lv Hou.

91
00:06:53,180 --> 00:06:54,660
That person is Prince Lv Hou,

92
00:06:54,940 --> 00:06:56,020
also known as Prince Song.

93
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:57,620
Liu Yiyi, Princess Consort Song,

94
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:59,180
is the eldest daughter of Minister Liu
of the Ministry of Revenue

95
00:06:59,580 --> 00:07:00,900
and also the granddaughter
of the Marquis of the West.

96
00:07:01,940 --> 00:07:03,620
Her strength can't be underestimated.

97
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:11,420
That's my fifth brother Lv Ke.

98
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:12,340
How to say that?

99
00:07:12,740 --> 00:07:13,620
He's also a huge deal.

100
00:07:14,140 --> 00:07:15,180
You will know later.

101
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:18,260
His wife is called Chu Ge,

102
00:07:18,540 --> 00:07:20,140
daughter of the concubine of Minister Chu
of the Ministry of Civil Affairs.

103
00:07:27,700 --> 00:07:28,540
Changsheng.

104
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:32,340
Yi'an.

105
00:07:35,020 --> 00:07:35,860
It's him.

106
00:07:42,260 --> 00:07:44,940
Changsheng, stop looking.
The banquet will begin.

107
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:46,580
Your country has so many rules.

108
00:07:47,260 --> 00:07:49,780
The Emperor is here.

109
00:07:53,340 --> 00:07:55,380
Father.

110
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:57,420
Sit down.

111
00:07:57,940 --> 00:07:59,860
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thanks, Father.

112
00:08:01,220 --> 00:08:02,700
Start the banquet.

113
00:08:11,980 --> 00:08:13,620
This barbarian princess

114
00:08:13,620 --> 00:08:14,740
can't even sit properly.

115
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,540
Look, Prince Qin even serves her food.

116
00:08:18,220 --> 00:08:20,260
Although Her Highness is not well-mannered,

117
00:08:20,540 --> 00:08:22,020
she's really beautiful.

118
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:23,860
Among all the people present,

119
00:08:23,860 --> 00:08:26,020
no other lady can outshine her.

120
00:08:26,020 --> 00:08:27,620
That's because Princess Royal didn't come.

121
00:08:27,620 --> 00:08:29,380
This barbarian

122
00:08:29,380 --> 00:08:30,700
is no match for

123
00:08:30,700 --> 00:08:32,100
Princess Royal's elegance.

124
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:33,940
In terms of nobility,

125
00:08:33,940 --> 00:08:34,980
she can't compare to Princess Royal.

126
00:08:35,700 --> 00:08:36,860
In terns of talent and knowledge,

127
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:38,100
she's not as good as Miss Rujing.

128
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:40,500
Only her face is worth mentioning.

129
00:08:41,180 --> 00:08:43,700
I don't know when Miss Rujing will come back.

130
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:45,900
After all, she grew up with Prince Qin.

131
00:08:45,900 --> 00:08:46,860
- They're childhood sweethearts.
- Xiao Zilv.

132
00:08:47,100 --> 00:08:49,580
We really should take
Princess Changsheng down a peg.

133
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:57,580
Father, I toast you.

134
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,780
I have heard that women in Fuyu

135
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:07,340
are not inferior to Great Tang's.

136
00:09:07,580 --> 00:09:08,580
The men are martial

137
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:09,660
and the women are good at dancing.

138
00:09:09,660 --> 00:09:11,900
Your Highness is a girl in a million.

139
00:09:11,900 --> 00:09:13,500
You must be excellent too.

140
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:15,020
Why don't you

141
00:09:15,020 --> 00:09:16,300
dance for us

142
00:09:16,780 --> 00:09:17,780
and let Father

143
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:18,980
appreciate your charm?

144
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:21,100
Very well.

145
00:09:21,100 --> 00:09:23,620
Would you show me

146
00:09:23,620 --> 00:09:25,580
the graceful dance of Fuyu?

147
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:31,060
Father.

148
00:09:31,660 --> 00:09:33,180
Today is Changsheng's welcome banquet.

149
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:35,140
Changsheng is the Princess of Fuyu

150
00:09:35,140 --> 00:09:36,420
and my unmarried wife.

151
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:38,100
This seems

152
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:39,500
not appropriate.

153
00:09:39,900 --> 00:09:41,180
My Great Tang

154
00:09:41,180 --> 00:09:42,340
is worshipped by all countries.

155
00:09:42,660 --> 00:09:43,500
What?

156
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:45,300
You don't want to?

157
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:47,140
Do you feel contempt

158
00:09:47,140 --> 00:09:48,580
for Great Tang?

159
00:09:49,340 --> 00:09:51,780
Princess Changsheng traveled
a long way to Great Tang

160
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:53,300
just to make an alliance through marriage.

161
00:09:53,820 --> 00:09:55,340
Some narrow-minded people

162
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:56,540
deliberately make things difficult for her,

163
00:09:57,020 --> 00:09:59,660
and even elevated this unspeakable rivalry

164
00:09:59,660 --> 00:10:00,980
to such a major deal.

165
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:03,540
You must be scheming

166
00:10:04,420 --> 00:10:05,900
to drive a wedge

167
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:07,220
between Great Tang and Fuyu.

168
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:09,140
Well...

169
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:20,460
Your Majesty.

170
00:10:20,900 --> 00:10:22,100
Our peace-making marriage

171
00:10:22,460 --> 00:10:23,700
received congratulations
from all over the world.

172
00:10:23,700 --> 00:10:24,940
Since the marriage has been decided,

173
00:10:24,940 --> 00:10:26,220
there is no distinction between host and guest,

174
00:10:26,420 --> 00:10:27,420
only the etiquette between
monarch and subject.

175
00:10:27,820 --> 00:10:28,820
I'm willing

176
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,020
to present a dance for you

177
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,300
as an entertainment.

178
00:10:31,940 --> 00:10:33,860
Good, good.

179
00:10:41,340 --> 00:10:43,020
Aren't those war drums?

180
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:45,340
Who knows what she's thinking?

181
00:11:16,340 --> 00:11:17,540
Trivial skills.

182
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:43,540
Good.

183
00:12:50,780 --> 00:12:51,620
Careful.

184
00:13:13,740 --> 00:13:15,220
The six peony paintings at the back

185
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:16,180
are dedicated to Your Majesty.

186
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:17,500
May Great Tang

187
00:13:17,860 --> 00:13:19,020
prosper forever

188
00:13:19,700 --> 00:13:20,620
and maintain good relations

189
00:13:20,620 --> 00:13:21,900
with Fuyu.

190
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:23,340
May Your Majesty

191
00:13:23,340 --> 00:13:24,420
live a long life.

192
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:26,420
Good, good.

193
00:13:27,100 --> 00:13:29,500
Reward Princess Changsheng

194
00:13:29,500 --> 00:13:30,940
with a pair of golden hairpins,

195
00:13:30,940 --> 00:13:32,220
100 ounces of gold,

196
00:13:32,220 --> 00:13:34,100
100 pieces of colorful

197
00:13:34,100 --> 00:13:35,140
gold silk cotton cloth.

198
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:36,660
Take a seat.

199
00:13:37,060 --> 00:13:38,140
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thanks, Father.

200
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:39,260
Come on.

201
00:13:39,340 --> 00:13:41,180
Let's toast to Changsheng.

202
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:44,340
Your Majesty.

203
00:13:44,340 --> 00:13:47,100
I have seen many beauties over the years.

204
00:13:47,100 --> 00:13:48,260
But Princess Changsheng

205
00:13:48,260 --> 00:13:50,020
is good-looking in an unconventional way.

206
00:13:50,420 --> 00:13:52,340
Prince Qin is also brave and battlewise.

207
00:13:52,700 --> 00:13:53,860
Now it seems

208
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:55,500
they're a match

209
00:13:55,780 --> 00:13:57,500
made in heaven.

210
00:13:57,940 --> 00:13:58,780
Yes.

211
00:13:58,860 --> 00:14:01,180
Princess Changsheng is both outstanding

212
00:14:01,180 --> 00:14:02,300
and pretty.

213
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:04,980
She also has an intelligent heart.

214
00:14:05,460 --> 00:14:07,860
We really feel ashamed of ourselves.

215
00:14:08,140 --> 00:14:10,460
Fuyu has a lot of good singers and dancers.

216
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:12,300
It's normal that

217
00:14:12,620 --> 00:14:13,580
their princess can dance.

218
00:14:15,300 --> 00:14:17,220
I know that I'm not well-informed.

219
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:19,100
The drum

220
00:14:19,420 --> 00:14:22,260
is always used on the battlefield.

221
00:14:22,260 --> 00:14:23,620
I've never seen

222
00:14:23,980 --> 00:14:25,140
a drum dance before.

223
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:28,420
Father.

224
00:14:29,460 --> 00:14:30,540
I think

225
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:32,140
there is something wrong with the drum dance.

226
00:14:33,500 --> 00:14:34,860
What's wrong?

227
00:14:35,220 --> 00:14:36,780
Princess Changsheng,

228
00:14:36,780 --> 00:14:37,820
were those

229
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:39,340
war drums that you used?

230
00:14:39,860 --> 00:14:41,140
All the generals know

231
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:43,860
the sound of the drums means to charge.

232
00:14:44,140 --> 00:14:45,980
Now the world is peaceful.

233
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:48,860
I wonder if she's referring to something.

234
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:56,940
Father, calm down.

235
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:58,180
Princess Changsheng

236
00:14:58,180 --> 00:14:59,300
didn't do it on purpose.

237
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:00,540
She is a woman

238
00:15:00,540 --> 00:15:01,980
and never been on the battlefield.

239
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:03,460
How could she know

240
00:15:03,460 --> 00:15:04,780
every time the drum is beaten,

241
00:15:04,780 --> 00:15:06,180
people would die?

242
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:07,580
She won't even know

243
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:08,740
that the very first drumming cheers them up,

244
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:09,940
the second weakens them,

245
00:15:09,940 --> 00:15:11,180
while the third absolutely devitalizes them.

246
00:15:12,940 --> 00:15:14,300
Well said,

247
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:15,820
steering clear of the crucial point.

248
00:15:16,460 --> 00:15:17,980
Just now Princess Changsheng
danced with the six drums,

249
00:15:18,180 --> 00:15:19,380
which means peace

250
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:20,500
will last forever in Great Tang.

251
00:15:28,540 --> 00:15:29,380
Changsheng.

252
00:15:29,940 --> 00:15:30,980
What do you say?

253
00:15:33,940 --> 00:15:35,780
It is said that Great Tang is prosperous

254
00:15:35,780 --> 00:15:36,740
and tolerant to diversity.

255
00:15:37,140 --> 00:15:38,020
I'm sure you understand

256
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:39,700
the purpose of my dance

257
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:40,900
is to remember the past

258
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:42,220
and bless the future.

259
00:15:42,220 --> 00:15:43,420
What does this mean?

260
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:44,500
It's been many years

261
00:15:44,660 --> 00:15:46,260
that the two armies fight against each other

262
00:15:46,260 --> 00:15:47,540
and the people suffer from war.

263
00:15:47,820 --> 00:15:48,660
Your Majesty is wise

264
00:15:48,660 --> 00:15:49,580
and advocates for peace.

265
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:51,140
This follows the laws of nature

266
00:15:51,580 --> 00:15:52,780
and complies with public opinion.

267
00:15:53,300 --> 00:15:55,460
I appreciate Your Majesty's broad-mindedness,

268
00:15:55,860 --> 00:15:57,060
so I presented this dance

269
00:15:57,540 --> 00:15:58,460
to commemorate

270
00:15:58,460 --> 00:16:00,180
the soldiers who died in war

271
00:16:00,380 --> 00:16:01,980
and the displaced people.

272
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,380
It is also a blessing

273
00:16:03,380 --> 00:16:04,820
of peace and prosperity

274
00:16:04,820 --> 00:16:06,180
under Your Majesty's rule.

275
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:08,180
May the country prosper

276
00:16:08,180 --> 00:16:09,300
and enjoys peace

277
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:10,340
and quiet.

278
00:16:10,340 --> 00:16:12,380
May the people of our two countries

279
00:16:12,380 --> 00:16:13,460
be friendly with each other

280
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:14,580
and live in harmony.

281
00:16:16,340 --> 00:16:17,180
I

282
00:16:17,540 --> 00:16:19,020
wish to guard Great Tang

283
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:20,060
and make sure

284
00:16:20,260 --> 00:16:21,300
we live in peace and prosperity

285
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:22,340
like Changsheng

286
00:16:22,580 --> 00:16:23,860
and you wish for.

287
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,460
Well said.

288
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:29,340
- I like Changsheng's drum dance...
- Princess.

289
