295
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:44,220
Great Tang's medical skills.

296
00:16:45,420 --> 00:16:47,100
He is the envoy of Fuyu.

297
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:52,020
Princess Royal.

298
00:16:52,260 --> 00:16:53,980
Aren't we going to the banquet?

299
00:16:55,740 --> 00:16:57,340
