314
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:30,540
(Prince Qin's Mansion)

315
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:33,980
Your Highness.

316
00:17:34,260 --> 00:17:35,100
I have

317
00:17:35,100 --> 00:17:36,740
sent someone to inspect it carefully.

318
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:38,460
It's just that

319
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:39,740
the banquet was crowded with people,

320
00:17:39,740 --> 00:17:41,300
