324
00:17:46,220 --> 00:17:47,420
Why do we need evidence

325
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:48,340
to punish them?

326
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:49,930
Yes.

327
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:50,820
Pass my order.

328
00:17:51,260 --> 00:17:52,180
Send more people

329
00:17:52,460 --> 00:17:54,180
