335
00:18:10,220 --> 00:18:11,380
waiting to go out to battle with you.

336
00:18:14,700 --> 00:18:15,940
The time is not yet ripe.

337
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:16,940
It can wait.

338
00:18:16,940 --> 00:18:18,860
The soldiers have almost recovered.

339
00:18:18,860 --> 00:18:20,060
Just wait for you to give the order.

340
00:18:20,540 --> 00:18:22,340
The situation is unstable now.

341
00:18:22,340 --> 00:18:23,940
Tall trees catch much wind.

342
00:18:24,140 --> 00:18:25,900
If we rashly send troops to attack Fuyu,

343
00:18:25,900 --> 00:18:26,860
with external problems,

344
00:18:27,380 --> 00:18:28,220
there'll be more trouble.

345
00:18:32,540 --> 00:18:34,780
Your Highness, Mr. Xiao has arrived.

346
00:18:37,340 --> 00:18:38,180
I know.

347
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:43,420
Why did you come?

348
00:18:43,780 --> 00:18:45,180
Don't stand. Please sit down.

349
00:18:46,860 --> 00:18:48,700
Should I address you

350
00:18:49,020 --> 00:18:49,980
as Prince Qin?

351
00:18:50,420 --> 00:18:51,620
You've come a long way

352
00:18:51,620 --> 00:18:52,700
to Great Tang.

353
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:54,140
You must think us very disorganized.

354
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:57,020
Youyong, get some tea.

355
00:18:58,460 --> 00:18:59,300
No need.

356
00:19:07,380 --> 00:19:08,900
What do you want

357
00:19:08,900 --> 00:19:09,740
to see me about?

358
00:19:10,140 --> 00:19:11,700
