367
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:34,020
Me and Changsheng

368
00:19:34,340 --> 00:19:35,500
have not gotten married yet,

369
00:19:36,820 --> 00:19:37,820
but Changsheng

370
00:19:37,820 --> 00:19:38,980
will be my

371
00:19:38,980 --> 00:19:40,300
legitimate wife.

372
00:19:40,620 --> 00:19:41,460
She's Princess Consort Qin

373
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:43,180
of Great Tang.

374
00:19:43,740 --> 00:19:44,580
Mr. Xiao.

375
00:19:44,980 --> 00:19:46,140
Why do you think

376
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:47,700
I will harm my wife?

377
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:50,060
Then why didn't you tell Changsheng

378
00:19:50,060 --> 00:19:50,980
your real identity?

379
00:19:51,620 --> 00:19:53,340
We'll spend the rest of our lives together.

380
00:19:53,820 --> 00:19:55,660
Since Changsheng no longer minds this,

381
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:57,580
there is no need for you to worry.

382
00:20:00,020 --> 00:20:00,860
Mr. Xiao.

383
00:20:02,980 --> 00:20:04,420
I would like to mention one more thing.

384
00:20:04,980 --> 00:20:07,100
If you miss someone, you miss them forever.

385
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:09,300
Even if you follow her to Great Tang,

386
00:20:09,860 --> 00:20:10,940
