387
00:20:11,500 --> 00:20:12,740
Better to let go.

388
00:20:20,420 --> 00:20:24,140
(Prince Qin's Mansion)

389
00:20:35,700 --> 00:20:36,580
Your Highness, sorry for the wait.

390
00:20:37,580 --> 00:20:38,420
Your Highness.

391
00:20:38,540 --> 00:20:39,500
Didn't I tell you?

392
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,740
You can be yourself in here.

393
00:20:42,060 --> 00:20:43,300
Don't be bound by these etiquettes.

394
00:20:46,380 --> 00:20:47,220
Your Highness.

395
00:20:47,460 --> 00:20:48,380
Did you find

396
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,860
who threw the marble?

397
00:20:49,860 --> 00:20:51,100
I have already found some clues.

398
00:20:51,660 --> 00:20:52,660
You don't have to

399
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:53,740
worry about this.

400
00:20:54,180 --> 00:20:55,500
I will definitely help you get justice.

401
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,020
Thanks.

402
00:20:58,700 --> 00:20:59,540
Then

403
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:00,740
I'll leave first.

404
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:02,700
Changsheng.

405
00:21:03,300 --> 00:21:04,140
Let's dine together

406
00:21:04,580 --> 00:21:05,420
