407
00:21:06,180 --> 00:21:07,420
Maybe tonight...

408
00:21:07,420 --> 00:21:08,260
I'll be waiting for you.

409
00:21:17,140 --> 00:21:18,420
These are Fuyu's dishes.

410
00:21:19,500 --> 00:21:20,900
Previously in Prince Changle's Mansion,

411
00:21:20,900 --> 00:21:22,380
I learned to cook a few dishes.

412
00:21:23,020 --> 00:21:23,860
You should try it

413
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:27,660
and see if it suits your taste.

414
00:21:28,780 --> 00:21:29,620
You made them?

415
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,900
(They don't taste bad.)

416
00:21:39,580 --> 00:21:40,660
The taste is not bad, right?

417
00:21:41,140 --> 00:21:42,180
You are sincere.

418
00:21:43,340 --> 00:21:45,260
Try this dish, "Regret".

419
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:47,020
That's not the name of this dish.

420
00:21:47,020 --> 00:21:48,420
It is not called this in Fuyu,

421
00:21:49,300 --> 00:21:50,340
but the name changed

422
00:21:50,700 --> 00:21:51,780
in Great Tang.

423
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:54,340
That way,

424
00:21:54,740 --> 00:21:56,020
