427
00:22:02,860 --> 00:22:03,700
What rules?

428
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:04,540
Tell me.

429
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:05,620
Don't deceive me.

430
00:22:05,860 --> 00:22:06,740
Don't distrust me.

431
00:22:07,020 --> 00:22:08,060
