432
00:22:08,700 --> 00:22:09,540
Understand?

433
00:22:10,740 --> 00:22:11,580
Understood.

434
00:22:12,220 --> 00:22:13,260
Whatever you say.

435
00:22:15,340 --> 00:22:16,180
But

436
00:22:16,740 --> 00:22:18,220
I also have a small request.

437
00:22:18,220 --> 00:22:19,060
Sure.

438
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:20,220
It depends on my mood whether I agree.

439
00:22:20,620 --> 00:22:21,620
Like you said,

440
00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:23,220
you and I are a couple,

441
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,420
