I'm only afraid that you don't trust me.

447
00:22:35,940 --> 00:22:36,780
I hope

448
00:22:36,940 --> 00:22:38,260
you can treat me as

449
00:22:38,260 --> 00:22:39,460
someone you can rely on.

450
00:22:45,580 --> 00:22:46,420
Okay.

451
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:47,420
I promise you.

452
00:23:10,660 --> 00:23:11,500
Again.

