00:24:38,260 --> 00:24:39,780
I help apply medicine to you

467
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:41,900
because

468
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:44,940
you cooked for me.

469
00:24:45,220 --> 00:24:47,060
But don't think

470
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,260
I can forgive you so easily.

