487
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:34,780
It has to be me?

488
00:25:35,420 --> 00:25:36,260
It has to be you.

489
00:25:37,580 --> 00:25:38,420
Changsheng.

490
00:25:38,860 --> 00:25:39,820
