00:26:29,420 --> 00:26:31,690
♪Year after year♪

514
00:26:31,990 --> 00:26:34,850
♪I just wish for a red line between my fingers♪

515
00:26:34,850 --> 00:26:36,500
♪The oath on the Three-Life Stone♪

516
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:39,800
