539
00:30:51,980 --> 00:30:54,180
Are you really not going
to take responsibility for me?

540
00:30:56,020 --> 00:30:57,460
I didn't do anything.

541
00:30:58,660 --> 00:31:00,140
Why should I take responsibility?

542
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:05,460
You didn't

543
00:31:06,380 --> 00:31:07,220
do anything?

544
00:31:08,060 --> 00:31:09,100
Last night,

545
00:31:09,100 --> 00:31:10,380
you got drunk.

546
00:31:10,380 --> 00:31:11,860
You asked me to take you back.

547
00:31:11,860 --> 00:31:12,740
I wanted to leave,

548
00:31:12,740 --> 00:31:13,860
