00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:43,860
Accident?

578
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:45,420
You haven't gotten married yet.

579
00:32:45,420 --> 00:32:47,180
Why is Prince Qin disregarding the rules?

580
00:32:48,180 --> 00:32:49,380
No, no.

581
00:32:49,700 --> 00:32:50,940
There's no accident.

582
00:32:51,140 --> 00:32:53,500
So that's not an accident.

583
00:32:53,700 --> 00:32:54,620
No.

584
00:32:56,460 --> 00:32:57,380
Don't ask anymore.

585
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:59,340
Nothing happened between us.

586
00:33:00,020 --> 00:33:00,900
Prepare the pen and ink.

587
00:33:01,540 --> 00:33:03,140
What do you want them for?

588
00:33:03,140 --> 00:33:04,060
Copy the Meditation Mantra.

589
00:33:13,580 --> 00:33:15,340
(Huadeng Pavilion)
Jinyan.

590
00:33:15,340 --> 00:33:17,420
Give me the copybook we brought from Fuyu.

591
00:33:18,420 --> 00:33:19,260
Okay.

592
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:29,780
You've been copying scriptures for two days.

593
00:33:29,780 --> 00:33:31,180
Still haven't calmed down yet?

594
00:33:32,820 --> 00:33:34,020
(Travel Far Away)

595
00:33:44,300 --> 00:33:46,500
Even though the grass withers,

596
00:33:46,900 --> 00:33:49,260
the fallen flowers will meet again elsewhere.

597
00:33:51,660 --> 00:33:53,540
After parting ways with old friends,

598
00:33:54,340 --> 00:33:56,340
I only wish for you to know me.

599
00:33:59,060 --> 00:34:01,260
I only wish for you to know me.

600
00:34:01,580 --> 00:34:03,260
Even though the grass withers,

601
00:34:03,260 --> 00:34:04,860
I only wish for you to know me.

602
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:07,420
This means Yi'an is Prince Qin.

603
00:34:07,660 --> 00:34:08,500
Liar.

604
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:29,940
Jinyan.

605
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,420
Have you heard

606
00:34:31,420 --> 00:34:33,020
the phrase "seeing things
reminds people of someone"?

607
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:34,340
I have heard,

608
00:34:34,340 --> 00:34:35,500
but I haven't seen it.

609
00:34:35,940 --> 00:34:36,900
But

610
00:34:36,900 --> 00:34:38,460
now I see it.

611
00:34:40,260 --> 00:34:41,420
What nonsense are you talking about?

612
00:34:41,420 --> 00:34:43,060
I just wrote something, what's wrong?

613
00:34:43,060 --> 00:34:44,020
Yes, yes.

614
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:45,180
You're just

615
00:34:45,180 --> 00:34:46,820
writing Prince Qin's poem

616
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:49,460
and thinking about Prince Qin.

617
00:34:49,780 --> 00:34:50,660
If you ask me,

618
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:52,180
just go see him if you want to.

619
00:34:52,780 --> 00:34:54,820
It's not like you are

620
00:34:54,820 --> 00:34:55,780
thousands of miles away.

621
00:34:56,020 --> 00:34:57,020
He's just next door.

622
00:35:00,660 --> 00:35:01,900
Who wants to see him?

623
00:35:01,900 --> 00:35:03,060
The last person I want to see

624
00:35:03,060 --> 00:35:03,900
is him.

625
00:35:04,060 --> 00:35:05,220
Yes, yes.

626
00:35:07,460 --> 00:35:08,300
Look at Her Highness.

627
00:35:08,500 --> 00:35:09,340
She's getting anxious.

628
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:17,140
Your Highness.

629
00:35:17,500 --> 00:35:18,540
Are you looking for someone?

630
00:35:20,180 --> 00:35:21,100
No.

631
00:35:21,980 --> 00:35:24,500
Are you looking for Prince Qin?

632
00:35:24,980 --> 00:35:26,300
I'm not.

633
00:35:26,300 --> 00:35:27,980
I heard Youyong say

634
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:29,860
His Highness is very busy recently.

635
00:35:30,060 --> 00:35:32,740
When he returns home,
he's always in the study to discuss work.

636
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,820
I've been copying scriptures lately,
and my limbs are sore.

637
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:40,980
I'll go there for a walk.

638
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:46,980
Your Highness, don't go far.

639
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:48,140
It's a gloomy day.

640
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:49,340
I'm afraid it's going to rain.

641
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:06,980
Princess Consort.

642
00:36:10,860 --> 00:36:12,220
I'm not that yet.

643
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:14,700
Whatever.

644
00:36:19,020 --> 00:36:20,420
Your Highness, what are you looking at?

645
00:36:22,180 --> 00:36:23,300
You're alone?

646
00:36:24,060 --> 00:36:25,300
Where's Youmou?

647
00:36:25,620 --> 00:36:27,060
He went to the training camp
to watch the new recruits.

648
00:36:27,460 --> 00:36:28,740
You want to see him?

649
00:36:28,740 --> 00:36:29,820
I can give him the message.

650
00:36:30,100 --> 00:36:31,020
It's okay.

651
00:36:31,540 --> 00:36:32,780
I'm just asking.

652
00:36:36,580 --> 00:36:38,860
This tree is growing well.

653
00:36:40,540 --> 00:36:41,380
Well,

654
00:36:42,140 --> 00:36:43,260
where is Prince Qin?

655
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:44,820
I want to ask him

656
00:36:44,820 --> 00:36:46,220
what kind of tree is this.

657
00:36:46,460 --> 00:36:47,540
It looks pretty good.

658
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:49,380
His Highness went to the palace
and hasn't returned yet.

659
00:36:49,660 --> 00:36:51,500
I'll ask him for you when he comes back.

660
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:53,020
No need.

661
00:36:53,540 --> 00:36:55,340
I'll ask him

662
00:36:55,340 --> 00:36:56,500
next time I see him.

663
00:37:22,020 --> 00:37:23,420
Your Highness, don't open the window.

664
00:37:23,420 --> 00:37:25,380
It's raining so hard tonight.

665
00:37:26,220 --> 00:37:28,020
This is the first time I've seen rain

666
00:37:28,020 --> 00:37:29,140
since I came to Luojing.

667
00:37:32,860 --> 00:37:33,700
Oh no.

668
00:37:34,060 --> 00:37:35,580
- What's wrong?
- Muyan trees.

669
00:37:35,900 --> 00:37:37,220
I never thought it would rain.

670
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,580
We didn't use protection.

671
00:37:38,580 --> 00:37:39,420
Now the Muyan trees

672
00:37:39,420 --> 00:37:40,740
will die from flooding.

673
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:42,900
I should have thought of it earlier.

674
00:37:44,940 --> 00:37:46,220
(Huadeng Pavilion)
Your Highness.

675
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:47,060
Your Highness.

676
00:37:48,860 --> 00:37:49,860
Your Highness, wait.

677
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:50,980
You haven't taken an umbrella.

678
00:37:55,140 --> 00:37:56,580
Your Highness, where are you going?

679
00:37:56,580 --> 00:37:58,180
- Muyan Forest.
- Now?

680
00:37:58,180 --> 00:37:59,660
Lend me the horse.

681
00:38:00,340 --> 00:38:01,860
Your Highness, don't go!

682
00:38:02,060 --> 00:38:03,060
The rain is too heavy.

683
00:38:03,980 --> 00:38:05,300
I'll go there for you.

684
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:07,460
- You don't know how to tend the trees.
- Your Highness.

685
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:09,740
- Take an umbrella.
- Your Highness.

686
00:38:11,020 --> 00:38:11,860
Your Highness.

687
00:38:12,740 --> 00:38:13,940
What can we do?

688
00:38:14,160 --> 00:38:15,100
I'm going after Her Highness.

689
00:38:15,100 --> 00:38:16,580
Hurry to the palace to report to His Highness.

690
00:38:16,580 --> 00:38:17,420
Okay.

691
00:38:20,580 --> 00:38:21,420
Let's go.

692
00:38:39,671 --> 00:38:44,741
♪Sitting alone in the west window,
quietly watching the snow♪

693
00:38:46,271 --> 00:38:52,361
♪Silently falling and piling up♪

694
00:38:53,021 --> 00:38:59,191
♪The red flowers can't stand the cold♪

695
00:39:00,481 --> 00:39:05,101
♪And withered at night♪

696
00:39:06,401 --> 00:39:11,671
♪Facing the freezing north wind♪

697
00:39:12,881 --> 00:39:19,331
♪Looking at you, it's hard to say goodbye♪

698
00:39:19,691 --> 00:39:26,291
♪I fear the heat will fade away in an instant♪

699
00:39:27,071 --> 00:39:33,281
♪The snow covers the night♪

700
00:39:35,391 --> 00:39:41,811
♪After the separation, it's hard to meet again♪

701
00:39:42,111 --> 00:39:48,601
♪Can't see through the ups and downs of fate♪

702
00:39:48,751 --> 00:39:55,651
♪Let the yearning for you run wild♪

703
00:39:56,261 --> 00:40:02,121
♪How can a lonely lamp comfort me♪

704
00:40:02,451 --> 00:40:09,201
♪The sky is dark, the moon is waning♪

705
00:40:09,631 --> 00:40:16,491
♪Hear my cry♪

706
00:40:32,411 --> 00:40:37,051
♪You're wearing a blue gown♪

707
00:40:39,671 --> 00:40:45,411
♪Spring breeze blowing♪

708
00:40:46,771 --> 00:40:52,501
♪Another year has passed♪
